688
01:10:00,630 --> 01:10:02,188
不在了
No.

689
01:10:04,000 --> 01:10:06,969
如果我想要檢查所有的房間
If I wanted to check the cabins, all 12 of them,

690
01:10:07,036 --> 01:10:08,298
我是不是需要搜查令呀
I'd need a warrant, wouldn't I?

691
01:10:08,371 --> 01:10:10,156
如果你不信的話  就跟我來吧
Listen, if you don't believe me, come on with me.

692
01:10:10,156 --> 01:10:11,272
你可以幫我換床單
You can help me change beds.

693
01:10:11,341 --> 01:10:13,901
不用了  多謝
Okay? Oh. no, thanks.

694
01:10:31,661 --> 01:10:33,356
改變主意了?
Change your mind?

695
01:10:36,599 --> 01:10:39,817
我...我想肯定是因為我的某些表情
You know, I... I think I must have one of those faces you just can't

696
01:10:39,817 --> 01:10:40,695
使得你不相信我的話
Help believing.

697
01:10:40,770 --> 01:10:42,567
-還有人在家嗎  -沒有
- Is anyone at home? - No.

698
01:10:42,639 --> 01:10:44,971
