Oh? There's somebody sitting up in the window.

699
01:10:45,041 --> 01:10:46,235
沒  沒有
No, no, there isn't.

700
01:10:46,309 --> 01:10:47,401
肯定有  你去瞧瞧
Sure, go ahead. Take a look.

701
01:10:47,477 --> 01:10:49,468
那肯定是我母親
Oh, that must be my mother.

702
01:10:49,546 --> 01:10:52,014
她是個病人
She's an invalid.

703
01:10:52,081 --> 01:10:54,072
實際上  她喜歡獨居
It's practically like living alone.

704
01:10:54,150 --> 01:10:55,640
明白
Oh, I see.

705
01:10:56,886 --> 01:10:59,786
如果這個女孩  曼璐﹒克蘭在這兒
Now, if this girl, Marion Crane, were here, you wouldn't

706
01:10:59,786 --> 01:11:01,289
你不會把她藏起來吧
Be hiding her, would you?

707
01:11:01,357 --> 01:11:03,723
-不會  -即使她出高價也不會嗎
- No. - Not even if she paid you well?

708
01:11:03,793 --> 01:11:04,851
不會
No.

709
01:11:05,528 --> 01:11:07,962
我們這樣說好了  我不想跟你爭論
Let's just say, just for the sake of argument,

710
01:11:08,031 --> 01:11:10,625
她想要你勇敢地保護她
That she wanted you to gallantly protect her.

711
01:11:10,700 --> 01:11:12,600
你知道你被利用了
You'd know that you were being used.

712
01:11:12,669 --> 01:11:13,966
你不會蠢到被耍吧
You wouldn't be made a fool of, would you?

713
01:11:14,037 --> 01:11:15,629
但我并不傻  我...
But I'm not a fool. well, I...

714
01:11:15,705 --> 01:11:18,765
我不能被別人愚弄  即便是被女人耍
And I'm not capable of being fooled, not even by a woman.

715
01:11:18,842 --> 01:11:20,070
這不是在詆毀你的男子氣概
Well, this is not a slur on your manhood.

716
01:11:20,143 --> 01:11:21,303
這么說吧
Let's put it this way.

717
01:11:21,377 --> 01:11:25,245
她可能耍了我  但她沒有耍我的母親
She might have fooled me, but she didn't fool my mother.

718
01:11:25,315 --> 01:11:27,249
那你母親見過她了?  我可以跟你母親談一下嗎
Well, then your mother met her. Could I talk to your mother?

719
01:11:27,317 --> 01:11:29,979
不行  如我之前跟你說的  她不見外人
No. As I told you, she's confined.

720
01:11:30,053 --> 01:11:31,350
知道  但就几分鐘而已
Yes, but just for a few minutes. That's all.

721
01:11:31,421 --> 01:11:33,514
可能會有你所遺漏的線索
There might be some hint that you missed out on.

722
01:11:33,590 --> 01:11:35,922
生病的老女人通常比較易怒
You know, sick old women are usually pretty sharp.

723
01:11:35,992 --> 01:11:37,459
阿伯蓋斯特先生...我想我已經...
Mr. Arbogast... I think I've...

724
01:11:37,527 --> 01:11:39,461
就一會兒  我不會觸怒她的
Just for a moment. I wouldn't disturb her.

725
01:11:39,729 --> 01:11:41,196
我想我已經都跟你說清楚了
I think I've talked to you all I want to.

726
01:11:41,264 --> 01:11:42,595
知道  但就...
Yes, but just for...

727
01:11:42,665 --> 01:11:45,566
我想如果你馬上離開就再好不過了  謝謝
I think it'd be much better if you left now. Thanks.

728
01:11:45,902 --> 01:11:47,802
好吧
Well, all right.

729
01:11:48,538 --> 01:11:51,769
如果你讓我跟她談一下肯定會讓我少走很多冤枉路
You sure would save me a lot of leg work if you'd let me talk to her.

730
01:11:51,841 --> 01:11:52,899
這也需要搜查令嗎
Would I need a warrant for that, too?

731
01:11:52,976 --> 01:11:54,204
當然
Sure.

732
01:11:55,411 --> 01:11:57,572
好吧  不管怎樣還是謝謝
All right. Thanks anyway.

733
01:12:51,768 --> 01:12:54,862
喂  盧密斯  我是阿伯蓋斯特  萊拉在嗎
Hello, Loomis. This is Arbogast. Is Lila there?

734
01:12:55,171 --> 01:12:57,332
好  請讓她聽電話
Okay. Let me talk to her, please.

735
01:12:58,775 --> 01:13:00,242
喂  萊拉
Hello, Lila.

736
01:13:00,910 --> 01:13:03,674
聽著  萊拉  曼璐來過這兒
Lila, listen. Marion was up here.

737
01:13:04,681 --> 01:13:07,377
是的  上個星期六晚上她在貝茨汽車旅館投宿
Yes, she spent last Saturday night at the Bates Motel.

738
01:13:07,450 --> 01:13:09,247
就在舊公路旁邊
It's right out here on the old highway.

739
01:13:09,319 --> 01:13:12,777
我連她住哪個房間都知道  是1號房
I even know what cabin she was in. It was number one.

740
01:13:13,511 --> 01:13:17,623
這個年輕的旅館老板說她只住了一晚
This young fella that runs the place said that she just spent the night,

741
01:13:17,694 --> 01:13:20,162
第二天就離開了  就這樣
Left the next day and that was it.

742
01:13:22,665 --> 01:13:24,360
還不大確定
No, not exactly.

743
01:13:25,535 --> 01:13:27,609
相信我  我確實盤問過他
Well, I did question him, believe me,

744
01:13:27,609 --> 01:13:29,972
但我認為我這趟沒白來
But I think I got all there was to get.

745
01:13:30,039 --> 01:13:33,236
我還得從這兒找點線索
I'll just have to pick up the pieces from here.

746
01:13:33,676 --> 01:13:37,237
說實話  我感覺不是很滿意...
Well, I tell you, I don't feel entirely satisfied...

747
01:13:37,313 --> 01:13:39,679
這個小伙子有個生病的老母親
See, this boy had a sick old mother.

748
01:13:39,749 --> 01:13:42,684
我想她見過曼璐并跟她說過話
I think she saw Marion and talked to her.

749
01:13:42,752 --> 01:13:45,983
沒有  遺憾地是他不讓我見她
No. No, unfortunately, he wouldn't let me see her.

750
01:13:46,422 --> 01:13:50,188
我有  但我想會先回汽車旅館
Well, I was, but I think I'll go back to the motel first.

751
01:13:51,194 --> 01:13:54,755
不用  你跟盧密斯待一起  我大概1小時內回去
No, you stay there with Loomis. I'll be back in about an hour.

752
01:13:54,831 --> 01:13:56,924
好的  聽著  我...
All right, fine. Listen, I...

753
01:13:57,000 --> 01:13:59,525
你知道我的想法會很高興的
You'll be happy to know what I think.

754
01:13:59,602 --> 01:14:03,595
我想我們的朋友薩姆﹒盧密斯并不知道曼璐來這兒
I think our friend Sam Loomis didn't know that Marion was here.

755
01:14:05,308 --> 01:14:08,436
好的  大概1小時左右見
Yeah. all right. See you in about an hour or less.

756
01:14:08,511 --> 01:14:09,535
好的  再見
All right, bye bye.

757
01:15:06,202 --> 01:15:07,430
貝茨?
Bates?

758
01:17:41,257 --> 01:17:43,817
有時寂寞的聲音會縈繞在周六的夜晚
Sometimes Saturday night has a lonely sound.

759
01:17:43,893 --> 01:17:45,986
有留意過嗎  萊拉
Ever notice that, Lila?

760
01:17:47,430 --> 01:17:49,694
薩姆  他說1小時左右
Sam, he said an hour or less.

761
01:17:50,299 --> 01:17:51,596
對
Yeah.

762
01:17:52,969 --> 01:17:54,664
已經過去3個小時了
It's been three.

763
01:17:54,737 --> 01:17:56,898
難道我們就這樣坐著干等嗎
Well, are we just going to sit here and wait?

764
01:17:56,973 --> 01:17:58,531
他會回來的
He'll be back.

765
01:17:58,941 --> 01:18:01,432
耐心等待吧
Let's sit still and hang on, okay?

766
01:18:06,749 --> 01:18:08,410
舊公路有多遠?
How far is the old highway?

767
01:18:08,484 --> 01:18:10,179
你不會想要出去吧
You wanna go out there, don't you?

768
01:18:10,253 --> 01:18:11,777
-找阿伯蓋斯特跟那個老太太算賬...  -是的
- Bust in on Arbogast and the old lady... - Yes.

769
01:18:11,854 --> 01:18:13,515
-或許搖醒她  -是的
- Maybe shake her up. - Yes!

770
01:18:13,589 --> 01:18:15,216
那可不是什么理智的行為
That wouldn't be a wise thing to do.

771
01:18:15,291 --> 01:18:17,054
在我的家族字典里沒有耐心兩字
Patience doesn't run in my family, Sam.

772
01:18:17,126 --> 01:18:18,753
-我要出去  -聽著  阿伯蓋斯特說過...
- I'm going out there. - Look, Arbogast said...

773
01:18:18,828 --> 01:18:20,728
1個小時左右嘛
An hour, or less.

774
01:18:25,468 --> 01:18:26,901
我走了
Well, I'm going.

775
01:18:26,969 --> 01:18:28,664
你會迷路的
You'll never find it.

776
01:18:32,575 --> 01:18:33,667
待在這兒
Stay here.

777
01:18:33,743 --> 01:18:34,903
為什么我不可以跟你一起去
Why can't I go with you?

778
01:18:34,977 --> 01:18:37,202
不知道  我們其中一個得留下
I don't know. One of us has to be here,

779
01:18:37,203 --> 01:18:38,743
說不定他已經在路上了
In case he's on the way.

780
01:18:38,814 --> 01:18:41,009
我該做些什么  就這樣坐著干等嗎
What am I supposed to do, just sit here and wait?

781
01:18:41,083 --> 01:18:42,914
對  待在這兒
Yeah. stay here.

782
01:19:03,639 --> 01:19:04,936
阿伯蓋斯特?
Arbogast?

783
01:19:06,309 --> 01:19:07,674
阿伯蓋斯特?
Arbogast!

784
01:19:10,947 --> 01:19:12,414
阿伯蓋斯特?
Arbogast!

785
01:19:42,545 --> 01:19:43,569
他還沒回來嗎
He didn't come back here?

786
01:19:43,646 --> 01:19:44,943
薩姆
Sam!

787
01:19:45,014 --> 01:19:48,575
阿伯蓋斯特跟貝茨都不在  只有一個老太太在家
No Arbogast, no Bates. Only the old lady at home.

788
01:19:48,651 --> 01:19:51,620
病老太沒法應門  或是不愿應門
Sick old lady unable to answer the door, or unwilling.

789
01:19:51,687 --> 01:19:53,655
他會去哪兒了呢
Where could he have gone?

790
01:19:53,723 --> 01:19:54,934
也許他找到了一些確切的線索
Maybe he got some definite lead.

791
01:19:54,935 --> 01:19:55,918
就直奔線索而去了
Maybe he went right on.

792
01:19:55,992 --> 01:19:57,118
不知會我一聲?
Without calling me?

793
01:19:57,193 --> 01:19:58,251
走得太急了
In a hurry.

794
01:19:58,327 --> 01:19:59,794
薩姆  當時他什么線索都沒有就打來了
Sam, he called when he had nothing.

795
01:19:59,795 --> 01:20:01,387
什么都沒  除了一股不滿意的感覺
Nothing but a dissatisfied feeling.

796
01:20:01,464 --> 01:20:05,161
你不認為如果他發現了什么會打給我們嗎
Don't you think he'd have called if he had anything at all?

797
01:20:05,801 --> 01:20:07,826
是的  我想他會打來
Yes, I think he would've.

798
01:20:07,903 --> 01:20:08,892
我們去見艾爾﹒錢伯斯吧
Let's go see Al Chambers.

799
01:20:08,971 --> 01:20:10,029
他是誰
Who's he?

800
01:20:10,106 --> 01:20:11,733
我們這兒的副警長
Our deputy sheriff around here.

801
01:20:11,807 --> 01:20:13,604
好的  我去拿外套
All right. Let me get my coat.

802
01:20:21,851 --> 01:20:23,318
晚上好
Good evening.

803
01:20:23,953 --> 01:20:27,889
不知道該從何說起  直接切入主題吧
Well, I don't know where to start, except at the beginning.

804
01:20:27,957 --> 01:20:29,049
好
Yes.

805
01:20:30,192 --> 01:20:31,181
這位是來自鳳凰城的萊拉﹒克蘭
This is Lila Crane from Phoenix.

806
01:20:31,260 --> 01:20:33,057
你好
How do you do?

807
01:20:33,162 --> 01:20:35,460
她來這兒是為了找她妹妹的
She's been here searching for her sister.

808
01:20:35,531 --> 01:20:38,159
請了一位私家偵探幫忙...
There's this private detective helping and...

809
01:20:38,234 --> 01:20:40,293
我們接到那個私家偵探打來的電話
Well, we got a call from this detective

810
01:20:40,369 --> 01:20:42,769
說他在那家舊公路旁的汽車旅館追查到她的消息
Saying that he'd traced her to that motel out on the old highway.

811
01:20:42,838 --> 01:20:44,806
那肯定是貝茨汽車旅館
That must be the Bates Motel.

812
01:20:44,874 --> 01:20:45,560
他查到她住過那兒
He traced her there

813
01:20:45,561 --> 01:20:47,775
然后打給我們說他要去盤問貝茨太太
and called us to say he was going to question Mrs.Bates.

814
01:20:47,843 --> 01:20:49,435
諾曼結婚了?
Norman took a wife?

815
01:20:49,512 --> 01:20:52,845
不是  我想沒有  是位老太太  他的母親
No, I don't think so. An old woman. His mother.

816
01:20:53,215 --> 01:20:54,718
不管是誰  自從挂完電話后
Well, anyway, that was early this evening.

817
01:20:54,719 --> 01:20:56,343
我們就跟他失去了聯系
We haven't seen or heard from him since.

818
01:20:56,419 --> 01:20:59,946
你妹妹失蹤多久了
Now, your sister's missing how long?

819
01:21:00,022 --> 01:21:03,219
到昨天為止  她已經失蹤1個星期了
Well, she left Phoenix a week ago yesterday, without a trace.

820
01:21:03,292 --> 01:21:06,784
你跟那位偵探怎么會追查到菲爾威爾的
How'd you and this detective come to trace her to Fairvale?

821
01:21:06,862 --> 01:21:09,057
他們以為她來找我了
They thought she'd be coming to me.

822
01:21:09,131 --> 01:21:10,257
她是獨自離開鳳凰城的嗎
Left Phoenix under her own steam?

823
01:21:10,332 --> 01:21:11,492
是的
Yes.

824
01:21:11,567 --> 01:21:14,161
她不像是失蹤倒像是逃跑
She's not missing so much as she's run away.

825
01:21:14,236 --> 01:21:15,294
對
That's right.

826
01:21:15,371 --> 01:21:16,497
為什么
From what?

827
01:21:19,475 --> 01:21:20,601
她偷了些錢
She stole some money.

828
01:21:20,676 --> 01:21:22,007
很多嗎
A lot?

829
01:21:24,046 --> 01:21:25,377
4萬塊錢
$40,000.

830
01:21:25,981 --> 01:21:27,573
那警方沒有...
And the police haven't been able to...

831
01:21:27,650 --> 01:21:28,997
大家考慮到...
Everyone concerned thought

832
01:21:28,998 --> 01:21:31,484
如果他們能讓她把錢還回去的話
If they could get her to give the money back,

833
01:21:31,554 --> 01:21:34,022
他們可以避免她被抓進警局
They could avoid involving her with the police.

834
01:21:34,090 --> 01:21:36,058
所以才請私家偵探
That explains the private detective.

835
01:21:36,059 --> 01:21:38,026
他追查到她曾住在貝茨旅館
He traced her to the Bates place.

836
01:21:38,094 --> 01:21:40,562
他打電話給你具體說了些什么
What exactly did he say when he called you?

837
01:21:40,663 --> 01:21:44,497
他說曼璐在那兒住了一晚就走了
Well, he said that Marion was there for one night and then she left.

838
01:21:44,567 --> 01:21:46,262
帶著4萬塊錢?
With the $40,000?

839
01:21:46,969 --> 01:21:49,096
錢的事他只字未提
Well, he didn't say anything about the money.

840
01:21:49,171 --> 01:21:51,571
電話內容無關緊要  是嗎
It isn't important what he said on the phone, is it?

841
01:21:51,640 --> 01:21:53,232
在他跟那位母親談完話之后
He was supposed to come back here and talk to us

842
01:21:53,309 --> 01:21:55,402
他本該回到這兒跟我們碰面  但他并沒回來
After he talked to the mother, and he didn't.

843
01:21:55,478 --> 01:21:57,708
所以我才找你介入調查此事
That's what I want you to do something about.

844
01:21:57,780 --> 01:21:59,270
調查什么
Like what?

845
01:22:00,149 --> 01:22:01,810
抱歉我說話急了點
I'm sorry if I seem overanxious.

846
01:22:01,884 --> 01:22:03,191
只是我敢肯定那兒
It's just that I'm sure there's

847
01:22:03,191 --> 01:22:05,581
有什么不對勁  并且我必須調查清楚
something wrong out there and I have to know what.

848
01:22:05,654 --> 01:22:07,966
我也覺得那兒不對勁
Well, I think there's something wrong too, Miss,

849
01:22:07,967 --> 01:22:09,146
但不是同一件事
but not the same thing.

850
01:22:09,225 --> 01:22:12,388
我想不對勁的是你的私家偵探
I think what's wrong is your private detective.

851
01:22:12,461 --> 01:22:16,488
我想他可能從諾曼﹒貝茨那兒
I think he got himself a hot lead as to where your sister was going,

852
01:22:16,565 --> 01:22:18,658
知道你妹妹去向的重要線索
Probably from Norman Bates,

853
01:22:18,734 --> 01:22:20,511
然后打給你  讓你們繼續等消息
And called you to keep you still

854
01:22:20,511 --> 01:22:22,898
而他就出發去追她和錢
While he took off after her and the money.

855
01:22:22,972 --> 01:22:26,840
不會的  他說他還沒調查清楚會再回來
No, no, he said he was dissatisfied and he was going back there.

856
01:22:26,909 --> 01:22:29,309
為什么不打給諾曼  問他說到底發生了什么事
Why don't you call Norman and let him say just what happened?

857
01:22:29,378 --> 01:22:30,743
現在嗎
At this hour?

858
01:22:30,813 --> 01:22:33,043
我剛從那兒回來  他出去了
Well, he was out when I was there just a while ago.

859
01:22:33,115 --> 01:22:35,174
如果他回來了  可能還沒睡
If he's back, he probably isn't even in bed yet.

860
01:22:35,251 --> 01:22:36,809
你去的時候他在家
He wasn't out when you were there,

861
01:22:36,886 --> 01:22:37,412
夜闌人靜
He just wasn't

862
01:22:37,412 --> 01:22:40,219
像某些人一樣  不應門罷了
answering the door in the dead of night, like some people do.

863
01:22:40,289 --> 01:22:42,553
這個小伙子像位隱士
This fellow lives like a hermit.

864
01:22:42,625 --> 01:22:45,753
你肯定還記得10年前發生的那件不幸的事
You must remember that bad business out there about 10 years ago.

865
01:22:45,828 --> 01:22:47,489
求你打一下吧
Please. Call.

866
01:22:53,736 --> 01:22:57,900
弗洛里  警長讓你連線貝茨汽車旅館
Florrie, the Sheriff wants you to connect him with the Bates Motel.

867
01:23:03,979 --> 01:23:06,573
喂  是諾曼嗎  我是錢伯斯警長
Hello, Norman? Sheriff Chambers.

868
01:23:08,250 --> 01:23:09,979
我很好  謝謝
I've been just fine, thanks.

869
01:23:10,052 --> 01:23:12,213
聽著  我們這兒出了點事
Listen, we got worries here.

870
01:23:12,821 --> 01:23:16,257
今晚是否有個男的去過你那兒
Yeah, have you had a fella stop by there tonight...

871
01:23:17,393 --> 01:23:19,759
他不是來投宿的
Well, this one wouldn't be a customer, anyway.

872
01:23:19,828 --> 01:23:21,125
他是位私家偵探  名字叫...
He's a private detective, name of...

873
01:23:21,197 --> 01:23:22,789
阿伯蓋斯特
Arbogast.

874
01:23:22,865 --> 01:23:24,423
叫阿伯蓋斯特
Arbogast.

875
01:23:27,970 --> 01:23:29,904
他離開之后呢
And after he left?

876
01:23:32,241 --> 01:23:34,072
沒關系  諾曼
No, that's okay, Norman.

877
01:23:36,145 --> 01:23:39,512
這位偵探去過那兒  諾曼跟他講了那個女孩的事
This detective was there, Norman told him about the girl,

878
01:23:39,582 --> 01:23:42,483
偵探謝過他之后就走了
The detective thanked him and he went away.

879
01:23:43,219 --> 01:23:46,484
他沒再回去嗎  他沒去見那位母親嗎
And he didn't come back? He didn't see the mother?

880
01:23:46,555 --> 01:23:48,819
你的偵探告訴你  他不能馬上回來
Your detective told you he couldn't come right back

881
01:23:48,891 --> 01:23:52,827
因為他要去盤問諾曼﹒貝茨的母親  是嗎
Because he was going to question Norman Bates's mother, right?

882
01:23:52,895 --> 01:23:54,021
是的
Yes.

883
01:23:54,663 --> 01:23:57,461
諾曼﹒貝茨的母親10年前就去世了
Norman Bates's mother has been dead and buried

884
01:23:57,533 --> 01:24:00,559
并安葬在綠色草坪墓地
In Green Lawn cemetery for the past 10 years.

885
01:24:02,071 --> 01:24:04,869
她被安葬時所穿的壽衣還是我幫諾曼選的
I helped Norman pick out the dress she was buried in.

886
01:24:04,870 --> 01:24:05,802
淺紫光藍色
Periwinkle blue.

887
01:24:05,874 --> 01:24:07,535
那不只是地方歷史事件
It ain't only local history, Sam.

888
01:24:07,610 --> 01:24:11,444
也是菲爾威爾地區唯一一起謀殺跟自殺案
It's the only case of murder and suicide on Fairvale Ledgers.

889
01:24:11,513 --> 01:24:15,973
當貝茨太太發現跟她交往的家伙已有家室
Mrs. Bates poisoned this guy she was involved with

890
01:24:16,051 --> 01:24:18,315
她就把他毒死了
When she found out he was married.

891
01:24:18,387 --> 01:24:21,481
然后她也服毒自殺了
Then took a helping of the same stuff herself.

892
01:24:21,557 --> 01:24:24,492
是番木鱉鹼  死得很難看
Strychnine. Ugly way to die.

893
01:24:25,494 --> 01:24:27,758
諾曼發現他們死在一起
Norman found them dead together.

894
01:24:27,830 --> 01:24:29,320
在床上
In bed.

895
01:24:30,432 --> 01:24:32,865
你是說我見到的那個坐在窗邊的老婦人
You mean that old woman I saw sitting in the window out there wasn't

896
01:24:32,865 --> 01:24:33,492
不是貝茨的母親嗎
Bates' mother?

897
01:24:33,569 --> 01:24:37,801
等等  薩姆  你肯定見過一位老婦人嗎
Now, wait a minute, Sam. Are you sure you saw an old woman?

898
01:24:37,873 --> 01:24:40,341
是的  在汽車旅館后面的房子里
Yes! In the house behind the motel!

899
01:24:40,409 --> 01:24:42,707
我去叫門  但她根本不理我
I called and pounded but she just ignored me!

900
01:24:42,778 --> 01:24:45,542
你是想告訴我  你見到了諾曼﹒貝茨的母親  對嗎
You want to tell me you saw Norman Bates' mother?

901
01:24:45,614 --> 01:24:48,845
但她肯定是  因為阿伯蓋斯特也這么說
But it had to be because Arbogast said so, too!

902
01:24:49,451 --> 01:24:52,614
那個年輕人不讓他去見她  是因為她病得很重
And the young man wouldn't let him see her because she was too ill.

903
01:24:52,688 --> 01:24:55,555
好吧  如果那位婦人是貝茨太太
Well, if the woman up there is Mrs. Bates,

904
01:24:56,892 --> 01:25:00,225
那埋在綠草坪墓地的又是誰呢
Who's that woman buried out in Green Lawn cemetery?

905
01:25:43,539 --> 01:25:46,940
母親  我現在要提出...
Now, mother, I'm gonna bring something up...

906
01:25:48,610 --> 01:25:49,872
抱歉  孩子
I am sorry, boy,

907
01:25:49,945 --> 01:25:53,608
但你命令我時  看起來確實很可笑
But you do manage to look ludicrous when you give me orders.

908
01:25:53,682 --> 01:25:55,309
求您了  母親
Please, mother.

909
01:25:55,384 --> 01:25:58,319
不行  我不會藏在果窖里
No! I will not hide in the fruit cellar.

910
01:25:59,722 --> 01:26:01,883
你覺得我瘋了  對嗎
You think I'm fruity, huh?

911
01:26:01,957 --> 01:26:04,084
我就待在這兒
I'm staying right here.

912
01:26:04,159 --> 01:26:06,992
這是我的房間  誰也別想把我趕走
This is my room and no one will drag me out of it,

913
01:26:07,129 --> 01:26:10,155
我無恥的兒子更不行
Least of all my big, bold son.

914
01:26:10,232 --> 01:26:11,358
他們會來這兒的  母親
They'll come now, mother.

915
01:26:11,433 --> 01:26:15,369
他跟蹤過那個姑娘  現在有人要跟蹤他
He came after the girl, and now someone will come after him.

916
01:26:15,437 --> 01:26:17,200
母親  求您了  几天就好
Mother, please, it's just for a few days.

917
01:26:17,272 --> 01:26:19,706
這樣他們就找不到您了
Just for a few days so they won't find you.

918
01:26:19,775 --> 01:26:21,709
几天就好嗎
Just for a few days?

919
01:26:22,044 --> 01:26:25,309
在這陰暗潮濕的果窖?  決不
In that dark, dank fruit cellar? No!

920
01:26:25,948 --> 01:26:29,315
你曾把我藏在那里  孩子  你休想再讓我去那兒了  絕不
You hid me there once, boy, and you won't do it again, not ever again!

921
01:26:29,385 --> 01:26:30,943
現在滾蛋
Now get out!

922
01:26:32,488 --> 01:26:34,353
我讓你滾蛋  小子
I told you to get out, boy.

923
01:26:34,423 --> 01:26:36,254
我把您抱下去  母親
I'll carry you, mother.

924
01:26:36,325 --> 01:26:39,294
諾曼  你想干什么
Norman, what do you think you're doing?

925
01:26:39,361 --> 01:26:42,592
別碰我  諾曼
Don't you touch me! Don't! Norman!

926
01:26:48,070 --> 01:26:51,233
把我放下  放下我  我自己能走
Put me down! Put me down! I can walk on my own.

927
01:26:59,648 --> 01:27:00,842
早上好  早上好
Good morning. Good morning.

928
01:27:00,916 --> 01:27:02,406
早上好
Good morning.

929
01:27:02,484 --> 01:27:04,782
如果您不介意  我們愿駕車帶您去那間旅館
We thought if you didn't mind, we'd drive out to that motel with you.

930
01:27:04,853 --> 01:27:05,877
他已經去過了
He's already been.

931
01:27:05,954 --> 01:27:07,148
在儀式之前離開的
Went out before service.

932
01:27:07,222 --> 01:27:08,382
你們倆吃過早餐了嗎
Did you two have breakfast?

933
01:27:08,457 --> 01:27:09,754
什么也沒發現嗎
You didn't find anything?

934
01:27:09,825 --> 01:27:12,760
沒有  我們別擋道
Nothing. Let's clear the way here.

935
01:27:13,595 --> 01:27:15,995
他說了什么關于我妹妹的事嗎
Well, what did he say about my sister?

936
01:27:16,064 --> 01:27:19,261
和他向你的偵探說的一樣  她用了匿名
Just what he told your detective, she used a fake name.

937
01:27:19,334 --> 01:27:20,562
我看過了登記簿
Saw the register myself.

938
01:27:20,636 --> 01:27:23,605
看過了整個地方  事實上  那小伙子一個人住在那兒
Saw the whole place, as a matter of fact. That boy's alone there.

939
01:27:23,672 --> 01:27:25,037
他母親不在嗎
No mother?

940
01:27:25,107 --> 01:27:26,665
肯定是你的幻覺  薩姆
You must have seen an illusion, Sam.

941
01:27:26,742 --> 01:27:29,643
我知道你不會產生幻覺
I know you're not the seeing illusion's type,

942
01:27:29,711 --> 01:27:32,202
但那兒沒有女人  而且我不相信鬼神之說
But no woman was there and I don't believe in ghosts,

943
01:27:32,281 --> 01:27:34,146
-就是這樣  -我仍然覺得那兒有...
- So there it is. - I still feel that there's something...

944
01:27:34,216 --> 01:27:37,845
我理解你的感受  很抱歉不能讓你好受些
Can see you do. I'm sorry l couldn't make you feel better.

945
01:27:37,920 --> 01:27:39,649
你今天下午來我辦公室
You want to come around to my office this afternoon

946
01:27:39,721 --> 01:27:42,849
填一份失蹤人口及遭遇搶劫的報告  這才是你要做的
And report a missing person and a theft, that's what you want to do.

947
01:27:42,925 --> 01:27:44,916
你越快把此事交由法辦
The sooner you drop this in the lap of the law,

948
01:27:44,993 --> 01:27:48,861
就越有可能快點找到你妹妹
That's the sooner you stand a chance of your sister being picked up.

949
01:27:48,931 --> 01:27:50,523
怎么樣
How about that?

950
01:27:51,066 --> 01:27:52,294
我不知道
I don't know.

951
01:27:52,367 --> 01:27:53,527
今天是周日
It's Sunday.

952
01:27:54,236 --> 01:27:56,727
晚飯時來我家填報告吧
Come on over to the house and do your reporting around dinnertime.

953
01:27:56,805 --> 01:27:58,602
這樣會比較好
It'll make it nicer.

954
01:27:59,174 --> 01:28:00,539
你也來吧  薩姆
You too, Sam.

955
01:28:00,609 --> 01:28:01,701
謝謝
Thank you.

956
01:28:03,912 --> 01:28:06,176
也許我真的會產生幻覺
Maybe I am the seeing illusions type.

957
01:28:06,248 --> 01:28:07,738
不  你不會
No, you're not.

958
01:28:08,884 --> 01:28:10,647
好吧  你想讓我把你送回旅館還是...
Well, you want me to drop you at the hotel or...

959
01:28:10,719 --> 01:28:11,743
薩姆
Sam.

960
01:28:11,820 --> 01:28:15,187
在沒親自去過那里之前  我不會罷休的
I still won't feel satisfied until I go out there.

961
01:28:16,425 --> 01:28:18,450
我也不會  走吧
Neither will I. Come on.

962
01:28:19,695 --> 01:28:23,927
我們最好想想到了那兒要怎么做
We better decide what we're gonna say or do when we walk in there.

963
01:28:23,999 --> 01:28:26,297
我們先去注冊結婚
We're going to register as man and wife.

964
01:28:26,368 --> 01:28:28,962
再去他那兒租間房
We're going to get shown to a cabin,

965
01:28:29,471 --> 01:28:33,373
之后我們要調查那兒的每個角落  從里到外
And then we're going to search every inch of the place, inside and out.

966
01:28:57,299 --> 01:28:59,096
我想知道諾曼﹒貝茨在哪兒隱居
I wonder where Norman Bates does his hermiting.

967
01:28:59,167 --> 01:29:01,658
有人在窗戶那兒  我看到窗帘動了
Someone's at that window. I just saw the curtain move.

968
01:29:01,737 --> 01:29:03,034
過來
Come on.

969
01:29:05,807 --> 01:29:07,035
什么事
Well?

970
01:29:07,109 --> 01:29:08,303
正想給你打電話
Just coming up to ring for you.

971
01:29:09,611 --> 01:29:10,942
我猜你們想住店
Suppose you want a room.

972
01:29:11,013 --> 01:29:12,776
我們本想直接去舊金山
We were gonna try to make it straight to San Francisco,

973
01:29:12,848 --> 01:29:14,975
但是我們看了看天
But we don't like the look of that sky.

974
01:29:15,050 --> 01:29:16,483
感覺馬上要變天了  對吧
Looks like a bad day coming, doesn't it?

975
01:29:16,552 --> 01:29:18,213
好吧
Okay.

976
01:29:25,060 --> 01:29:26,220
我帶你們去10號房間
I'll take you to cabin 10.

977
01:29:26,295 --> 01:29:27,626
我們最好還是先登記  對吧
Better sign in first, hadn't we?

978
01:29:27,696 --> 01:29:29,630
不  沒必要
No. That's not necessary.

979
01:29:29,698 --> 01:29:33,725
我的老板會為此次旅行買單  90%可以報銷
My boss is paying for this trip and, well, it's 90% business.

980
01:29:33,802 --> 01:29:36,566
但他需要正式發票
He wants practically notarized receipts.

981
01:29:36,638 --> 01:29:39,266
我們最好登記  并拿到發票
I'd better sign in and get a receipt.

982
01:29:56,992 --> 01:29:58,357
謝謝
Thank you.

983
01:30:02,197 --> 01:30:04,631
-我幫你們去拿行李  -我們沒行李
- I'll get your bags. - Haven't any.

984
01:30:07,169 --> 01:30:08,500
那我帶你們看一下房間
I'll show you the room, then.

985
01:30:08,570 --> 01:30:10,333
頭回看到你這么開旅店
First time I've ever seen it happen.

986
01:30:10,405 --> 01:30:12,373
在美國的其他旅店  沒有行李的旅客必須登記
You check in any other place in this country without bags

987
01:30:12,441 --> 01:30:14,500
而且要付定金
And you have to pay in advance.

988
01:30:14,576 --> 01:30:15,804
10美元
$10.

989
01:30:23,352 --> 01:30:24,876
我的發票
That receipt.

990
01:30:30,826 --> 01:30:32,555
我先去看看
I'll go on ahead.

991
01:30:38,200 --> 01:30:41,294
好了  這是您的發票  那么  我來給您帶路
All right, there's your receipt. Now, I'll show you the cabin.

992
01:30:41,370 --> 01:30:44,066
不麻煩了  我們自己能找到
Don't bother yourself. We'll find it.

993
01:31:02,658 --> 01:31:04,455
薩姆  我們必須去調查那個房間
Sam, we have to go into that cabin and search it,

994
01:31:04,526 --> 01:31:08,053
無論我們多么害怕  或者付出多大代價
No matter what we're afraid of finding or how much it may hurt.

995
01:31:08,130 --> 01:31:09,358
知道了
I know.

996
01:31:09,931 --> 01:31:11,694
如果真有事  你覺得那兒會是事發地點嗎
Do you think if something happened, it happened there?

997
01:31:11,767 --> 01:31:13,257
我不知道
I don't know.

998
01:31:13,602 --> 01:31:16,093
但如果你有一家這樣不賺錢的旅店
But if you had a useless business like this motel,

999
01:31:16,171 --> 01:31:17,365
需要什么把它脫手
What would you need to get out?

1000
01:31:17,439 --> 01:31:19,498
然后在別的地方再開一家新的呢
To get a new business somewhere else?

1001
01:31:19,574 --> 01:31:20,939
4萬塊錢?
$40,000?

1002
01:31:23,645 --> 01:31:25,772
你如何証明這點
How could we prove that...

1003
01:31:25,847 --> 01:31:28,441
如果他在新高速路上開了家汽車旅店  一年后...
Well, if he opens a motel on the new highway in, say, a year...

1004
01:31:28,517 --> 01:31:31,008
這兒一定有証據
There must be some proof that exists now,

1005
01:31:31,086 --> 01:31:34,647
一定有能証明他搶走了曼璐錢的証據
Something that proves he got that money away from Marion somehow.

1006
01:31:34,723 --> 01:31:36,247
你憑什么那么肯定
What makes you sound so certain?

1007
01:31:36,324 --> 01:31:38,349
阿伯蓋斯特  她喜歡我  薩姆
Arbogast. He liked me, Sam.

1008
