在沼澤里  這次犯罪源于人格分裂  而非圖財
The swamp. These were crimes of passion, not profit.

1166
01:47:08,422 --> 01:47:12,153
他覺得有點冷  我能把毯子給他嗎
He feels a little chill. Can I bring him this blanket?

1167
01:47:12,226 --> 01:47:14,194
當然  可以
Oh, sure. All right.

1168
01:47:26,607 --> 01:47:28,598
謝謝
Thank you.

1169
01:47:35,616 --> 01:47:38,847
當一位母親不得不譴責自己的兒子時
It's sad when a mother has to speak the words

1170
01:47:38,919 --> 01:47:40,944
是多么悲哀啊
That condemn her own son,

1171
01:47:41,022 --> 01:47:44,856
但我不會讓他們認為是我殺的人
But I couldn't allow them to believe that I would commit murder,

1172
01:47:44,925 --> 01:47:48,759
他們會拋棄他的  就像我數年前應該做的那樣
They'll put him away now, as I should have years ago,

1173
01:47:49,497 --> 01:47:51,624
他一向很壞
He was always bad,

1174
01:47:51,699 --> 01:47:56,727
最終  他打算告訴警察是我殺的那些女孩和那個男人
And in the end he intended to tell them I killed those girls and that man,

1175
01:47:56,804 --> 01:48:00,570
除了端坐和凝視外  我什么也做不了
As if I could do anything except just sit and stare,

1176
01:48:00,641 --> 01:48:03,041
就像他的標本鳥一樣
Like one of his stuffed birds,

1177
01:48:03,811 --> 01:48:07,303
他們知道  我連手指都動不了  而且我也不會
They know I can't even move a finger, and I won't,

1178
01:48:07,381 --> 01:48:12,978
我只會在這里靜靜端坐  以免被人懷疑
I'll just sit here and be quiet, just in case they do suspect me,

1179
01:48:15,990 --> 01:48:19,255
他們大概會監視我  好吧  讓他們看吧
They're probably watching me, well, let them,

1180
01:48:19,827 --> 01:48:22,660
讓他們看看我是什么樣的人
Let them see what kind of a person I am,

1181
01:48:23,864 --> 01:48:26,332
我甚至不會拍死這只蒼蠅
I'm not even gonna swat that fly,

1182
01:48:26,400 --> 01:48:29,130
我希望他們在監視我  他們就會看到
I hope they are watching, they'll see,

1183
01:48:29,637 --> 01:48:31,332
他們會看到并且明白
They'll see and they'll know,

1184
01:48:31,405 --> 01:48:35,933
之后  他們會說"為什么  她連蒼蠅都不愿傷害啊"
And they'll say, ''why, she wouldn't even harm a fly, ''

